  "texts": [
    "One promising direction is to augment LLMs with a pre-built knowledge base containing comprehensive information on software dependencies, vulnerabilities, and best practices.",
    "In this setup, when a software update is identified, developers or security practitioners could use the RAG-based LLM system to query the knowledge base and receive tailored security recommendations for the specific dependencies involved.",
    "This approach would empower users to make more informed decisions, ensuring more effective and secure management of software dependencies.",
    "Additionally, developing a benchmark dataset specifically for evaluating AI-driven dependency management approaches is crucial.",
    "This dataset would allow researchers to systematically assess the effectiveness of RAG-based LLMs in real-world scenarios, identifying gaps and opportunities for improvement."
  ],
